Problem Statement 1


Colaberry Chat was built to connect the Colaberry Community all in one place. Students, Interns, mentors and Alumni are monitoring the chat. The goal is to have a 1st response time under 3 hrs.  The 1st response time now is about 2 days. The goal is to get the 1st Response time down to 3 hrs
